<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="256">Taxon</emphasis>
41: 555. 1992) and this was eventually approved by the General Committee (see review of the history of this proposal by Barrie, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="256">l.c.</emphasis>
55: 795-796. 2006).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageNumber="256" type="multiple">
