<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="256">Revised Handb. Fl. Ceylon</emphasis>
1: 38. 1980) restricted his original type choice (1974) to one of the specimens on p. 69, his earlier unrestricted choice appeared in the conservation proposal and the conserved type is therefore listed in the Vienna Code (2006) in this way.
</paragraph>
